Chelsea Signs Valencia Winger Juan Mata to Five-Year Contract

-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 
2011-08-24T16:45:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-24/chelsea-signs-valencia-winger-juan-mata-to-five-year-contract.html
Chelsea signed Valencia winger Juan
Mata to a five-year contract, the Premier League club said on
its website.  Mata scored 43 goals in 179 games over the past four
seasons with Valencia. The 23-year-old becomes the fourth
signing for new Blues manager Andre Villas-Boas, after Oriol
Romeu, Romelua Lukaku and Thibaut Courtois.  Mata has made 11 appearances for the Spanish national team.
He also captained  Spain  to the title at the Under-21 European
Championship this summer.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  